{"id":232939527,"title":"真心愛著我的貓","content":"最近冬天很冷\n我租的房子地板很冰 要窩進被窩裡才會暖\n但是貓貓除了睡覺之外她會在房間裡亂逛\n難免會冷 一直在想說想買暖爐給她\n但是真的沒什麼錢\n\n直到某天她打噴嚏了 還兩下\n我嚇到心臟都要跳出來了\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/d42e15d8-b831-4c27-b08a-9ccf45e87684/1280.jpeg\n所以直接買了一台小台的暖風機 也很便宜顆顆\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/31793b99-0225-46d6-8c55-c29a0fd2e807/1280.jpeg\n-\n收到當天貓貓很喜歡 躺著馬上睡得很舒服\n不然之前都靠著我縮成一團或是鑽被窩\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/93645c5d-0d66-4e3d-a3ac-5ee392ba8651/1280.jpeg\n給大家看她的心得感想 記得開聲音喔 她有講話\nhttps://www.dcard.tw/v2/vivid/videos/4717aabc-11a6-40fc-9b65-494e51a0efcb?r=1.7777777777777777\n我邊摸她邊看著她很舒服的樣子 打從心底覺得\n我真的好愛她喔 我心裡暖暖的覺得什麼事都無所謂了只要她健康快樂就好\n真是暖 有妳真好(⁎⁍̴̛ᴗ⁍̴̛⁎)\n祝大家新年快樂喔 好好愛護毛小孩❤️","excerpt":"最近冬天很冷，我租的房子地板很冰 要窩進被窩裡才會暖，但是貓貓除了睡覺之外她會在房間裡亂逛，難免會冷 一直在想說想買暖爐給她，但是真的沒什麼錢，直到某天她打噴嚏了 還兩下，我嚇到心臟都要跳出來了，所以","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"7ee21581-1307-4ba9-b9dc-82028bdcca49","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-22T14:26:03.254Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-22T14:26:03.254Z","commentCount":16,"likeCount":653,"tags":[],"topics":["貓","愛很大","不是喝水那個愛很大","愛很大就對了"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"寵物","forumAlias":"pet","school":"國立澎湖科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":648},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":5}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":true,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/d42e15d8-b831-4c27-b08a-9ccf45e87684/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/31793b99-0225-46d6-8c55-c29a0fd2e807/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/93645c5d-0d66-4e3d-a3ac-5ee392ba8651/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://vivid.dcard.tw/Public/4717aabc-11a6-40fc-9b65-494e51a0efcb/thumbnail.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{